{
  "stem": "10835.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "In fact, my father, being that he worked at his tailoring profession, he-- we-- we had some customers who were butchers.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we were able to get meat beside the rations.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You know, you have some connections, you are able to manage.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And somehow we-- we did pretty good.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We did not-- we didn't-- as young people, you don't anticipate terrible-- a terrible future.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You just take it day by day.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we just-- we just waited to see what's going to happen.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But then in their winter of 1941, they deported the Poles first.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "All the Poles were deported.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They just were notified one day that they have to leave the next day.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they just had to leave.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "In fact, the town where we lived in then, Oswiecim, that part of the town was before the river Sola, which later on became Birkenau, which in Polish was called Brzezinka That's where the railroad station was, where they later brought in all these people.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Anyway, a few weeks-- didn't know what to think about it, since they deported Poles and they left Jews.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Somehow it was like curious.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then in March, they notified the Jews that they have to move out of this part of town and go across the river into the main town of Oswiecim, which we had to do.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We had no way to move.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We carried pieces of furniture.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Everybody carried a different thing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I remember I carried a mirror across the river.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We took apart the beds, and every child took a different piece of furniture.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we just-- well, took it-- we went on foot.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We-- we-- no, we took it into town.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the Jewish committee, which was called [NON-ENGLISH], arranged for accommodations, for living accommodations.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
